snippet.title: Wobbledogs Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wobbledogs is a new pet sim game from Tom Astle, published by Secret Mode which features colourful mutating dogs! Customise your Wobbledog, breed new Wobbledogs, and raise them as your own Wobbly friends!

After SIX YEARS of game development and one year in early access, Wobbledogs is coming to Steam 15th of March!

It's still available to buy and play on Steam in early access before it's release, so be sure to click here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1424330/Wobbledogs/
